Pushover push notification plugin for OPNsense.

Sends alerts via the Pushover API for a wide range of system events:
gateway up/down, WireGuard and OpenVPN tunnel state, Unbound DNS and
DHCP service health, CPU temperature, fan failures, firmware updates,
UPS events via apcupsd, system reboots, and configuration changes.

Adds a Services > Pushover page to the OPNsense web UI with per-monitor
toggles and configurable thresholds.

WWW: https://pushover.net
